-- Reliance Infrastructure Says Directors Will Respond to Regulator's Queries
-- Arijit Ghosh
-- 2010-08-03T02:39:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-03/reliance-infrastructure-says-directors-will-respond-to-regulator-s-queries.html

          
          
             Reliance Infrastructure Ltd. and
Reliance Natural Resources Ltd. will comply with the market
regulator’s process after the Securities & Exchange Board of
India issued an order asking its directors to reply to its
questions, according to a statement.  
 The companies “are confident of suitable resolution of the
matter, as legally advised,” Reliance Infrastructure said in
the e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        